    "NIKE (US)": "耐克公司",
    "Nike, Inc. is a major publicly traded sportswear and equipment supplier based in the United States. It is the world's leading supplier of athletic shoes and apparel and a major manufacturer of sports equipment with revenue in excess of $18.6 billion USD in its fiscal year 2008 . As of 2008, it employed more than 30,000 people worldwide. The company was founded on January 25, 1964 as Blue Ribbon Sports by Bill Bowerman and Philip Knight, and officially became Nike, Inc. in 1978. The company takes its name from Nike (Greek Νίκη pronounced [níːkɛː]), the Greek goddess of victory; it is also based on Egyptian usage of \"strength\", \"victory\", nakht. Nike markets its products under its own brand as well as Nike Golf, Nike Pro, Nike+, Air Jordan, Nike Skateboarding and subsidiaries including Cole Haan, Hurley International, Umbro and Converse. In addition to manufacturing sportswear and equipment, the company operates retail stores under the Niketown name.": "耐克公司是一家总部位于美国的主要上市运动服和设备供应商。它是世界领先的运动鞋和服装以及运动装备的主要制造商，在其2008财年的收入超过$ 18.6十亿美元的供应商。截至2008年，其全球员工超过30,000人。",
    "Trading Hours Mon – Fri 15:00 – 19:00": "交易时间周一 - 周五15:00 - 19点",
    "FACEBOOK": "脸书（FACEBOOK）",
    "Facebook is a social networking service launched in February 2004, owned and operated by Facebook, Inc. As of September 2012, Facebook has over one billion active users, more than half of them using Facebook on a mobile device. According to Social Media Today, in April 2010 an estimated 41.6% of the U.S. population had a Facebook account. Nevertheless, Facebook's market growth started to stall in some regions, with the site losing 7 million active users in the United States and Canada in May 2011.": "Facebook是在2004年2月推出的，拥有和经营的脸谱，公司作为2012年9月的一个社交网络服务，Facebook拥有超过十亿活跃用户，超过在移动设备上使用Facebook的一半。",
    "Trading Hours: US, Mon – Fri 14:40 – 21:10 GMT": "美国，周一 - 周五14:40 - 21:10 GMT",
    "GOOGLE (US)": "谷歌公司",
    "Google Inc. is an American public corporation, earning revenue from advertising related to its Internet search, e-mail, online mapping, office productivity, social networking, etc. Google has also developed an open source web browser and a mobile operating system. As of March 31, 2009 (2009-03-31), the company has 19,786 full-time employees. The company is running millions of servers worldwide, which process hundreds of millions of search requests each day.": "谷歌公司是美国的公众公司，从收入与它的互联网搜索，电子邮件，在线地图，办公效率，社交网络等的广告收入谷歌还开发了一个开源Web浏览器和移动操作系统。",
