    "TOPIX": "东证指数",
    "Tokyo stock Price Index, commonly known as TOPIX, along with Nikkei 225, is an important stock market index for the Tokyo Stock Exchange in Japan, tracking all domestic companies of the exchange's First Section. It is calculated and published by the TSE. As of February 1, 2011, there are 1,669 companies listed on the First Section of the TSE. The market value for the index on the same date is 197,401 Billion Yen.": "东京股票价格指数通常也被成为东证指数，与日经平均指数一起是日本东京证券交易所最重要的股票市价指数，跟踪所有东京证交所市场一部上市的所有日本企业（由TSE统计和发布的）。 2011年2月1日，有1669家企业被列在TSE的市场一部中。同一天的市价指数是197.401万亿日元。",
